title: Rush - The Hartford '90, CT 5-8-90 (m4a)
description:
Here is an excellent soundboard recording of Rush during their "Presto" tour. The beginning of "Force Ten" is cut, but other than that, this is a complete show. Hartford, CT 05-08-90 (m4a):

DISC 1:
Force Ten (Cut)
Freewill
Distant Early Warning
Time Stand Still
Subdivisions
Marathon
Red Barchetta
Superconductor
Show Don't Tell
The Pass
Closer To The Heart

DISC 2:
Manhattan Project
Xanadu
YYZ
Drum Solo
Scars
War Paint
Mission
Tom Sawyer
The Spirit Of Radio
2112 Overture
La Villa Strangiato
In The Mood
Wipeout/Jazz Bass


Lineup:
Geddy Lee - vocals, bass, keyboards
Alex Lifeson - guitars, vocals
Neil Peart - drums, percussion
